{"tid":366283,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"話解放軍會鎮壓香港人真係on99","createTime":"2017-08-20T02:01:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T08:21:28.000Z","uid":12231,"like":67,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9b8368e309dbaea80bccd7f3b4995f1c0d006b80","tid":366283,"uid":12231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T02:01:10.000Z","msg":"你估而家1989年咩，咁撚大件事都好似俾人抺粉筆字咁咩！？<br />\n<br />\n而家2017年，如果解放軍開槍鎮壓香港人，世界各地的傳媒實報導，中國政府的國際地位實跌到谷底。<br />\n<br />\n所以，都唔好聽到解放軍就縮沙，反而佢地更害怕大家手中的手機。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">今日，企出來！</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">自己民主自己爭取</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f1104a21ace3b0a378839452a3062415d2e1c26","tid":366283,"uid":12231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T02:09:57.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"944f46338ec9ef84292129f7ac83ba291d0d81bb","tid":366283,"uid":12231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T02:12:03.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b8f40a21ce22479e076cf7a58b3cd400f93149a","tid":366283,"uid":12231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T02:12:48.000Z","msg":"推俾多啲人睇"},{"pid":"c8f3bc57274b5763cb1f535a45f5647e2466150d","tid":366283,"uid":46688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T02:13:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8961623d4f119d77afffc0498043e6bc0e6b5dff","tid":366283,"uid":72990,"like":3,"dislike":11,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T02:14:18.000Z","msg":"要返工不了 <br />\n你洗唔洗返工呀?<br />\n要就收聲啦鍵盤打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=